<li>You can ask to correct your personal information if it is incomplete, inaccurate or outdated;</li>
<li>You can ask to anonymize, block or delete your personal information if we have no legal ground to collect or use your personal information;</li>
<li>If we share information with other organisations, you can ask for more information on that;</li>
<li>You have the right to revoke consent if you have given consent for the collection and use of your personal information. Also, you can ask for more information on the possibility of not providing consent and what will happen if you withdraw or deny consent.</li>
</ul>
<p>If you want to exercise any of your rights, you can contact our Data Protection Officer in Brazil. The contact details can be found in the Contact Us section.</p>
